These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, water
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, climbing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | 7up | fanta | water   |
| Sport      | lacrosse    | climbing  | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, water
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, colombian, russian
1. the pakistani is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the colombian is on the far left##1
3. the colombian is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | milk | juice     | water      |
| Nationality   | colombian | pakistani | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: pumpkin, kiwi, pomegranate
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | milk | mirinda  | juice       |
| Food       | pumpkin     | kiwi | pomegranate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, peach, watermelon
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, reading, chess
1. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | watermelon    | peach     | broccoli |
| Hobby   | chess | video-games | reading     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, horse
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, bus, bike
1. the person driving the bus is the owner of the horse##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | dog | chinchilla     | horse |
| Transport   | bike        | helicopter | bus    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: orange, onion, radish
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, airplane
1. the person eating orange is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person eating onion is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person eating radish is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | radish | orange      | onion  |
| Transport   | scooter       | quad-bike | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, trance, pop
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake, hamster
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of country##1
2. the fan of trance is the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | country     | trance    |
| Pet           | hedgehog | hamster | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, carrot
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, photography
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person eating kale is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | carrot | blueberry | kale      |
| Hobby   | woodworking     | photography | drawing |

