.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, woodworking, video-games
3 different pets are kept: snake, fish, frog
1. the owner of the snake is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | dancing  |
| Pet     | frog     | snake      | fish |

