.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, mirinda
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, family, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | coffee   | 7up    | mirinda    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | fantasy | musical |

