1. the fan of techno is the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the egyptian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | techno   | disco  |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | indonesian | brazilian |

