.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: grapes, kale, pepper
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, doctor, software-developer
1. the doctor is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating pepper is in the middle##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | grapes     | pepper   | kale     |
| Job    | software-developer | doctor | engineer |

