3 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the police-officer##1
2. the police-officer is on the left of the paramedic##1
3. the paramedic is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | entrepreneur    | police-officer | paramedic |
| Pet   | dog | rabbit     | goldfish        |

