.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, electronic, dubstep
1. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | tea  | hot-chocolate | fanta  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep   | punk |

