1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | video-games | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | metal     | classical  |

