.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, apricot, mango
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, tennis, rowing
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person eating peas##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | mango | peas       | apricot  |
| Sport   | rowing  | tennis | water-polo |

 